529
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:38,240
Get it?

530
00:33:38,279 --> 00:33:40,200
What operation?

531
00:33:45,559 --> 00:33:47,519
Those are a good idea.

532
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:54,720
This factory is in Berlin.
