535
00:33:59,079 --> 00:34:01,599
The Soviets reached
this facility before we did,

536
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:03,240
and we lost the damn thing.

537
00:34:05,480 --> 00:34:07,519
The routing orders
at the Pentagon,

538
00:34:07,559 --> 00:34:09,679
