quite simply,

554
00:34:59,559 --> 00:35:03,159
the best natural code-breaker
I have ever seen.

555
00:35:08,039 --> 00:35:11,360
What exactly is it
that you would like me to do?

556
00:35:16,199 --> 00:35:19,079
Commit this list
of periodicals to memory.

557
00:35:20,679 --> 00:35:24,039
Scan each new issue,
find any hidden codes,

558
00:35:24,119 --> 00:35:25,719
decipher them.

559
00:35:27,239 --> 00:35:29,760
Place your chin
on the chin rest.

560
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:33,440
