circling overhead,
you know how it is.

594
00:38:17,719 --> 00:38:19,719
No, I expect
that you wouldn't-

595
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:21,440
you wouldn't know, uh-

596
00:38:23,679 --> 00:38:26,239
If you leave your address
with my office,

597
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:29,280
