598
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:31,800
and we'll eat.

599
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:41,079
One more thing.
Do you have a name,

600
00:38:41,159 --> 00:38:43,519
or should I just
keep calling you "Miss"?

601
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:46,559
Governor,

602
00:38:46,639 --> 00:38:49,039
