628
00:40:36,559 --> 00:40:38,159
Oh, thank you.

629
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,800
Thank you for that.

630
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:43,119
No, keep it.

631
00:40:43,199 --> 00:40:46,280
