633
00:40:48,199 --> 00:40:50,039
No.

634
00:40:50,119 --> 00:40:52,000
I don't believe in luck.

635
00:40:56,199 --> 00:40:58,639
But I do believe
in assigning value to things.

636
00:40:59,599 --> 00:41:01,360
Oh.

637
00:41:08,519 --> 00:41:10,880
