to count them all.

638
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:16,480
I actually made it
to 4,348.

639
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:20,760
You are exceptionally odd.

640
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:23,559
I bet you're very
popular with the girls.

641
00:41:28,679 --> 00:41:31,039
A pair of odd ducks, then.

642
00:41:31,079 --> 00:41:33,599
Mmm.

643
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:38,000
Pick a shape.

644
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:40,920
What?

645
00:41:41,960 --> 00:41:45,039
Pick a shape.
An animal-
anything.

646
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:48,920
Okay.

647
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:51,400
