too drunk to drive.

690
00:48:00,280 --> 00:48:02,599
So, I took her in.

691
00:48:03,480 --> 00:48:07,079
She's so small.
She's young, John.
That's how they come.

692
00:48:09,159 --> 00:48:11,079
I'm at Harvard...

693
00:48:11,159 --> 00:48:13,760
doing the great
author's workshop.

694
00:48:13,800 --> 00:48:15,800
D.H. bloody Lawrence.

695
00:48:15,880 --> 00:48:17,920
I really do think you should
buy yourself a new book.

696
00:48:20,039 --> 00:48:22,960
Well, I've been reading
a lot about you.

697
00:48:23,920 --> 00:48:26,079
