any details.

701
00:48:34,760 --> 00:48:36,960
Top secret?
Black bag? Black ops?

702
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:39,079
Something like that.

703
00:48:39,159 --> 00:48:42,719
And, uh...
Yes?

704
00:48:42,760 --> 00:48:44,639
Well, l- I met a girl.

705
00:48:44,679 --> 00:48:47,519
No! A human girl?
Homo sapiens.

706
00:48:47,559 --> 00:48:49,639
A biped?
Yup. And contrary
to all probabilities,

707
00:48:49,719 --> 00:48:51,599
