for sure?

717
00:49:16,039 --> 00:49:19,320
Nothing's ever for sure, John.

718
00:49:19,400 --> 00:49:21,360
That's the only
sure thing I do know.

719
00:49:28,079 --> 00:49:30,000
Good evening.

720
00:49:36,039 --> 00:49:38,400
Alicia, please don't
be angry.

721
00:49:38,440 --> 00:49:39,920
I just lost track
of time at work...

722
00:49:41,000 --> 00:49:43,000
again.
Mm-hmm.

723
00:49:43,079 --> 00:49:45,400
I'm sorry.

724
00:49:46,519 --> 00:49:48,320
I didn't have time
to wrap it.

725
00:49:48,360 --> 00:49:50,760
Happy birthday.

726
00:49:54,920 --> 00:49:56,840
The refractive faces
of the glass, you see,

727
00:49:56,920 --> 00:49:58,679
