a full wavelength dispersal,

728
00:49:58,760 --> 00:50:00,639
so if you look inside it,
you can see-

729
00:50:00,719 --> 00:50:03,239
- Every possible color.
- Every possible color.

730
00:50:03,320 --> 00:50:04,679
Yeah.

731
00:50:04,760 --> 00:50:07,039
Remember you said that time
God must be a painter,

732
00:50:07,079 --> 00:50:09,760
because of all the colors,
at the governor's house?

733
00:50:09,840 --> 00:50:11,559
you said that.

734
00:50:11,639 --> 00:50:13,719
I didn't think
you were listening.

735
00:50:16,079 --> 00:50:18,079
