relationship warrant
long-term commitment?

738
00:50:44,920 --> 00:50:46,599
'Cause I need
some kind of proof,

739
00:50:46,679 --> 00:50:48,800
some kind of verifiable,
empirical data.

740
00:50:54,280 --> 00:50:57,239
