just give me a moment...

741
00:50:58,679 --> 00:51:01,559
to redefine
my girlish notions
of romance.

742
00:51:04,719 --> 00:51:06,840
A proof?

743
00:51:06,920 --> 00:51:08,440
Verifiable data.

744
00:51:08,519 --> 00:51:11,039
Um... okay.

745
00:51:12,920 --> 00:51:16,480
Well, how big
is the universe?

746
00:51:16,559 --> 00:51:18,079
Infinite.

747
00:51:18,159 --> 00:51:19,360
How do you know?

748
00:51:19,400 --> 00:51:21,119
I know because
all the data indicate it.

749
00:51:21,159 --> 00:51:22,840
But it hasn't
been proven yet?
No.

750
00:51:22,920 --> 00:51:24,639
You haven't seen it.
How do you know for sure?

751
00:51:24,719 --> 00:51:27,559
I don't, I just believe it.

752
00:51:27,599 --> 00:51:29,119
Mmm.

753
00:51:30,639 --> 00:51:32,800
It's the same
with love, I guess.

754
00:51:40,079 --> 00:51:41,639
Now,

755
00:51:41,719 --> 00:51:43,760
the part that
you don't know...

756
00:51:45,840 --> 00:51:48,559
is if I want
to marry you.

757
00:52:08,599 --> 00:52:10,760
Smile for the camera!

758
00:52:13,800 --> 00:52:15,239
Well done!

759
00:52:15,320 --> 00:52:17,159
Oh, sweet pea.

760
00:52:17,239 --> 00:52:18,880
I love you.
Congratulations.

761
00:52:18,920 --> 00:52:20,639
Hey, Sol.

762
00:52:20,679 --> 00:52:22,840
You look beautiful.

763
00:52:23,880 --> 00:52:25,039
Hi, how are you?

764
00:52:29,559 --> 00:52:31,679
Hey, Sol.

765
00:52:31,760 --> 00:52:33,639
Bye bye. Bye, now.

766
00:52:33,719 --> 00:52:35,639
- Bye!
- Bye!

767
00:52:35,719 --> 00:52:37,280
Be safe!

768
00:53:05,239 --> 00:53:07,000
Get in.
Hurry.

769
00:53:10,280 --> 00:53:13,079
They're following us.

770
00:53:16,519 --> 00:53:18,039
Who's-
Who's following us?

771
00:53:18,119 --> 00:53:19,679
The drop's been
compromised.

772
00:53:19,719 --> 00:53:21,559
- Get down!

773
00:53:22,679 --> 00:53:24,559
- Stay down.

774
00:53:50,599 --> 00:53:53,280
- Here, take this.
- I ain't shooting anybody.

775
00:53:53,360 --> 00:53:55,960
- Take the goddamn gun!
- No!

776
00:53:56,039 --> 00:53:57,559
Son of a-

777
00:54:13,480 --> 00:54:15,519
You stay back.
Don't move.

778
00:55:00,440 --> 00:55:02,719
John?

779
00:55:08,679 --> 00:55:10,079
Hi.

780
00:55:12,400 --> 00:55:14,039
